summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Latona Avenue from East Seventy-seventh Street to East Eighty-fifth Street, in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete sidewalks and under Ordinance No. 25112, creating Local Improvement District No. 2397 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
